    <title>顾史说</title>
    <link>https://cnily.me/posts/wenyan/gushi-shuo/</link>
    <pubDate>Wed, 30 Nov 2022 18:41:26 &#43;0800</pubDate><author>
                        <name>Cnily03</name><uri>https://github.com/Cnily03</uri><email>contact@cnily.me</email></author><guid>https://cnily.me/posts/wenyan/gushi-shuo/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<p>夫闻第千年以来，九土临有尧舜之芳躅、六飞之从骑，故土蒙罹黄河之决水、胡马之铁蹄。其尽万般而一族，历千患而同域，素不闻远洋之异肤，雅不识坤與之洲陆。故自鸦片之耻端，轮甲子而故步；更戊戌之新政，觉秦制而烂柯。时神州之义旗纷举而不能改其索，街巷之火光交错而不能除其弊；修齐治平难以中兴，我戕自缢寻以当道。盖非革命之循史，必有新义，又何救亡之乏术哉？</p>]]></description>
</item><item>
    <title>观党史怀古二首</title>
    <link>https://cnily.me/posts/wenyan/poetry/guandangshi-huaigu/</link>
    <pubDate>Thu, 22 Sep 2022 21:31:00 &#43;0800</pubDate><author>
                        <name>Cnily03</name><uri>https://github.com/Cnily03</uri><email>contact@cnily.me</email></author><guid>https://cnily.me/posts/wenyan/poetry/guandangshi-huaigu/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[其一：厦倾神器借天光，烈火播荃覆五洋。……其二：金瓯初日补霞光，共产德兴诩莽洋。……]]></description>
</item><item>
    <title>先怀来思赋</title>
    <link>https://cnily.me/posts/wenyan/xianhuai-laisi-fu/</link>
    <pubDate>Wed, 21 Sep 2022 22:33:57 &#43;0800</pubDate><author>
                        <name>Cnily03</name><uri>https://github.com/Cnily03</uri><email>contact@cnily.me</email></author><guid>https://cnily.me/posts/wenyan/xianhuai-laisi-fu/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[凤下千仞，麒麟穆立。莺鸾从舞，乾元康泰。天子本然，女娲所降于乾坤；士气排然，刈钁所驰于田塍。夫党发轫于荆棘，斩虺于三界。淬水火而炼其钢，钟四海而聚其流。兢兢业业，盖建纲于工农之基；浩浩汤汤，故策勋于颓危之际。旦则并马列于尧舜，夕则骋雄狮于江河。旂旌震扬于华夏，貔貅复怒于神州。]]></description>
</item><item>
    <title>有山先生论</title>
    <link>https://cnily.me/posts/wenyan/ysxs-lun/</link>
    <pubDate>Sun, 09 May 2021 17:17:30 &#43;0800</pubDate><author>
                        <name>Cnily03</name><uri>https://github.com/Cnily03</uri><email>contact@cnily.me</email></author><guid>https://cnily.me/posts/wenyan/ysxs-lun/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<p>有山先生者，吾所敬也，盖以身心之求乎先生之所处世，而力不从者，诚以所遇所经而不可效也。而吾独旌其所处世，以为有古之遗风存焉，<strong>而斯亦所遇所经就之也</strong>。</p>]]></description>
